          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Optimize and Automate Your Environment to Deliver a Scalable And Effective Testing Approach"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Perform Software Upgrades, Troubleshooting, Onboarding And Comprehensive Testing of Applications"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Validate Findings And Work With Development Teams and Provide Remediation Recommendations"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Integrate With Source Code Management, Ide, Ticketing, Monitoring and Incident Response Platforms"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Your AppSec solutions require significant bandwidth and the right skill set to properly manage. Our Application Security as a Service offering scales up or down based on your unique requirements for application security—from leveraging our team to help with implementation or integration assistance to full application security program support. Our Application Security as a Service program can help you:"
